components.name: Start Pipeline
components.description: Marks the entry point of the pipeline execution.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the first task.

components.name: Ingest USEast Sales Data
components.description: Extracts sales data for the USEast region from regional CSV files.

components.name: Ingest USWest Sales Data
components.description: Extracts sales data for the USWest region from regional CSV files.

components.name: Ingest EU Sales Data
components.description: Extracts sales data for the European region from regional CSV files.

components.name: Ingest APAC Sales Data
components.description: Extracts sales data for the APAC region from regional CSV files.

components.name: Convert USEast Currency to USD
components.description: Normalises USEast sales data to USD (noop for already USD data).

components.name: Convert USWest Currency to USD
components.description: Normalises USWest sales data to USD (noop for already USD data).

components.name: Convert EU Currency to USD
components.description: Converts European sales data from EUR to USD using a fixed exchange rate.

components.name: Convert APAC Currency to USD
components.description: Converts APAC sales data from JPY to USD using a fixed exchange rate.

components.name: Aggregate Global Revenue
components.description: Combines all regional converted sales data into a single global revenue CSV report.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after all four currency conversion tasks have completed successfully.

components.name: End Pipeline
components.description: Marks successful completion of the pipeline after aggregation.
